OOC: Ok, lets say Epyon was hit by the shots before to took off.

::Epyon::

He looked down to see electric blasts coming at him. He soared around
behind Rampage avoiding the blasts. He came down fast and hard, a karate
kick heading for Rampage's back.

::Hot Rod::

He saw the missile that came from no where(cloaked Double Punch), and
shot it down. He had to keep CliffJumper safe wile he was getting
repaired.
